Author: mayolespa
Text: I just recently relapsed these past few weeks and I noticed in the beginning when I ate maintenance and then began restriction the weight was coming off faster. I've been living off shirataki noodles, iced tea, and 2 ingredient pancakes. I used to have the same issues, just try not to think too hard about it :)
